ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb96f95c04b265d9f3b460914a6fa438e02a447","tid":1874974,"uid":45285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"根本攪個人崇拜就係傻仔既行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀，我就係講嗰班侵粉呀，侵侵話香港示威者係暴徒時都仲要幫佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2160e60904f8f44b06aa41dea69679d25a27b4","tid":1874974,"uid":124899,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"吓。佢無親政府播<br />\n<br />\n佢只係好似神探加里略果種，只對事件有興趣，對人無興趣果種人。"},{"pid":"3c857f7632e454b15d1d0b55d214a2a85481c64d","tid":1874974,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"推少d廢文 focus翻重要嘅野好過 係咪想光復香港㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOowZpL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOowZpL.png&h=8c2863cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特區政府（又稱港共傀儡政權）由組成到管治都毫無正當性。 港人應學委內瑞拉，自組港人政府，再予美國及西方承認<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"578b8eb9fff30f3c90cf79aa05ee3b926b8c3aaf","tid":1874974,"uid":295863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"無以為過喎"},{"pid":"9ece57413ab752d4b8c03d33501b2e608576783a","tid":1874974,"uid":342909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a2160e60904f8f44b06aa41dea69679d25a27b4","tid":1874974,"uid":124899,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"吓。佢無親政府播<br />\n<br />\n佢只係好似神探加里略果種，只對事件有興趣，對人無興趣果種人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"讚成 佢似係齋鍾意做research嗰啲"},{"pid":"26eeedf89e106f486ad20d52e5b49bcb5d0ec0b2","tid":1874974,"uid":125174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2160e60904f8